# Copy to .env.local and set for a CDN-hosted pyramid.
#
# Absolute base URL where the height-tile pyramid (manifest.json + tiles/) is
# served. Unset → the viewer loads the app-bundled public/pyramid/ (fine for a
# regional build, but the ~1 GB world build is too big to bundle and should live
# on object storage + CDN). The CDN must send CORS headers (the voxel worker
# fetches tiles cross-origin) and may gzip/brotli at the edge.
#
# VITE_TILE_BASE=https://cdn.example.com/pyramid/
